{"name":"Feint","type":"talent","img":"icons/skills/melee/sword-twirl-orange.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor can throw her target off-balance with a fake attack, followed up by a real one. She may burn 3 MP <em>before</em> making a melee or missile (but not magic) attack for the potential to do more damage. If her attack is successful, she makes a Deception skill check with the same task difficulty as her attack roll and adds each hit to the damage.&nbsp;</p>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.iZRqZ5tBvT68lU5j"}},"_id":"krGwvNaJjUs6y6h8"}
{"name":"Ascetic Armor","type":"talent","img":"icons/equipment/shield/heater-crystal-blue.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor's extreme discipline and bodily mastery makes her resilient to harm, so long as she doesn't weaken herself by relying on material defenses. This is a tiered talent that gets stronger every time it is purchased.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>I) Stoneskin - So long as her outfit's DR remains at 0, the actor gains a natural 1 DR that is <em>not</em> ignored by magic or environmental hazards (i.e. acid, fire, etc.).</li>\n<li>II) Mithrilskin - The natural DR provided by Stoneskin increases to 2 DR.</li>\n<li>III) Diamondskin - The natural DR provided by Stone\u0002skin increases to 3 DR.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>While this talent can render an actor effectively <em>immune</em> to acid, fire, etc., this natural resistance breaks down fairly quickly under prolonged exposure. If a player is relying on this talent to brave prolonged exposure to an environmental hazard (e.g. walking into a burning building), assume it only works for a number of rounds equal to the DR it provides.</p>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":true,"tiers":3,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.wL6ppsi8CQ1TyBLb"}},"_id":"lVnne17UMuCbmRdx"}
{"name":"Nature's Wrath","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-sparks-blue.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor can imbue her destructive magics with the power of the elements. She can burn an extra 1 MP when casting Kill Bolt or Kill Ball to imbue the spell with either fire, electricity, or ice (i.e. slow), all of which are discussed in the \"Environmental Hazards\" section of the \"Combat\" chapter.</p>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.MHvDjvxQu5RXWADy"}},"_id":"mTHCEE3lYRIBsRko"}
{"name":"Insult to Injury","type":"talent","img":"icons/skills/targeting/crosshair-mark-rough-pink.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor can leverage her medical understanding of anatomy to maximize the lethality of her attacks. She may burn 3 MP <em>before</em> making a melee or missile (but not magic) attack for the potential to do more damage. If her attack is successful, she makes a Medicine skill check with the same task difficulty as her attack roll and adds each hit to the damage.</p>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.k2OccI2s5QmhxY0N"}},"_id":"nZ7k1nZCNrMgSAXo"}
{"name":"Head Movement","type":"talent","img":"icons/skills/movement/feet-winged-sandals-tan.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor is skilled at staying just out of her opposition's reach while drawing them in for a counter attack. She may burn 3 MP <em>before</em> making a melee or missile (but not magic) attack for the potential to do more damage. If her attack is successful, she makes an Escape Artistry skill check with the same task difficulty as her attack roll and adds each hit to the damage.</p>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9xTfxckUieMCx5w6"}},"_id":"oewwEbozL8yuyBHa"}
{"name":"Throwing Arm","type":"talent","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/dagger-ringed-steel.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor can throw things to a great distance. The actor's thrown missile range for aerodynamic items (i.e. bombs, all weapons with the balanced rule, etc.) is long instead of medium. For all other objects, her thrown missile range is medium instead of short.</p>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Pqr41PItVmvIFV4o"}},"_id":"omD6rcjyTK4YJuM4"}
{"name":"Martial Artist","type":"talent","img":"icons/skills/movement/arrow-upward-yellow.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor has mastered an unarmed combat technique that relies on refined movement, technical blocks, and using an aggressor&rsquo;s own momentum against them. She may use her Dexterity attribute, instead of her Strength attribute, to make Unarmed Melee skill checks.</p>","purchaseCost":10,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.MSYNs34jn816jlJi"}},"_id":"pDZhZbWpf1KqgzoO"}
{"name":"Bloodletter","type":"talent","img":"icons/skills/wounds/injury-triple-slash-bleed.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor is particularly skilled at striking vital organs and weak points in armor when equipped with piercing weap\u0002ons, upgrading the damage of Precise Melee attacks by 1. This talent can be purchased up to 3 times.</p>","purchaseCost":20,"tiered":true,"tiers":3,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZvK5dGqkYPt7G9CM"}},"_id":"pnsCPIrRtWK7Obih"}
{"name":"Imposing Figure","type":"talent","img":"icons/skills/social/intimidation-impressing.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor has such a large and imposing physique that her size itself is enough to intimidate others. She may use her Strength attribute, instead of her Presence attribute, to make Menace skill checks.</p>","purchaseCost":10,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.0d9SULphf5hIJPoV"}},"_id":"ponDZ1CsUFgKgxMq"}
{"name":"Fog Wraith","type":"talent","img":"icons/creatures/magical/spirit-fear-energy-pink.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor is extremely dangerous when exploiting the literal fog of war. When she makes a sneak attack while hiding within the cover of a smoke bomb or the <em>sunblotter petals</em> aspect of the Bloom Blessing cantrip, add +2 to the damage she inflicts.</p>","purchaseCost":20,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.O7ZT90LaF3LK0FK6"}},"_id":"r5MKsBXTlOTV8eoD"}
{"name":"Anticipator","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/perception/eye-ringed-green.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor is always thinking several moves ahead of her opposition, intuiting her foes' next course of action long before they've decided on one. She may burn 3 MP <em>before</em> making a melee or missile (but not magic) attack for the potential to do more damage. If her attack is successful, she makes a Query skill check with the same task difficulty as her attack roll and adds each hit to the damage.</p>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.fuWls1bYGJGEhihJ"}},"_id":"revXVmGqAfyjbUHo"}
{"name":"Maintenance","type":"talent","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor spends her every spare moment sharpening, tightening and otherwise maintaining her weapons to keep them all in tip-top shape. She may burn 3 MP <em>before</em> making a melee or missile (but not magic) attack for the potential to do more damage. If her attack is successful, she makes a Craft skill check with the same task difficulty as her attack roll and adds each hit to the damage.&nbsp;</p>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.nwGcRIqN6ixdR8gd"}},"_id":"sd08y6sxm0x3rFnh"}
{"name":"Critical Critter","type":"talent","img":"icons/creatures/abilities/mouth-teeth-rows-red.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor's familiar is especially brutal when sicced upon its person's enemies, upgrading the damage of attacks and talents that leverage the Beast Ken skill (e.g. Battle Buddy, Pet Sortie, etc.) by 1. This talent can be purchased up to 3 times.</p>","purchaseCost":20,"tiered":true,"tiers":3,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.LQnpZU090lJOwkFv"}},"_id":"skS0owtiQkzKQTrj"}
{"name":"Tincturist","type":"talent","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-bottle-corked-labeled-green.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor has a tailor-made tincture for every occasion. At will, she can consume a weak healing potion (ignoring its effects) or a weak poison (ignoring its effects), but treat it as if she instead imbibed a performance-enhancing potion that converts a single fate dice into an attribute dice on her next roll. The effect does not stack by consuming more potions, though it can be used in conjunction with the Adept talent. This talent may only be used a number of times equal to the actor's Alchemy rating between each session of downtime.</p>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ARfbBt2y2w2ClBQY"}},"_id":"u9psVIEo0rfG7wiR"}
{"name":"Ascetic Assault","type":"talent","img":"icons/skills/melee/unarmed-punch-fist-yellow-red.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor's lifelong dedication to mastery of the martial arts makes her as lethal, unarmed, as a seasoned warrior wielding a weapon. This is a tiered talent that gets stronger every time it is purchased.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>I) Stonefist - The actor's unarmed attacks (including those made with unarmed melee like punching daggers) do +1 base damage and gain the <em>kinetic</em> rule.</li>\n<li>II) Snarestrike - The actor no longer needs to choose between an unarmed melee attack and a grapple attempt. If she scores at least 1 damage with an unarmed melee attack, she can choose to enter a grapple with her target.</li>\n<li>III) Heartquake - When the actor is already in a grapple at the beginning of her turn, her unarmed melee attacks against the target she is grappling with ignore DR.</li>\n</ul>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":true,"tiers":3,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PUgxScFcBTMtQfiA"}},"_id":"uucAEHVfhh0Bl8kW"}
{"name":"Brave Steed","type":"talent","img":"icons/environment/creatures/horse-brown.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor has a loyal mount. This talent exists to give players a means of acquiring a mount for their character via UPs instead of negotiating for assets with other players. Similar to familiars, this mount is quickly replaced in the narrative if it dies. This is a tiered talent that gets stronger every time it is purchased.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>I) Galloper Mount - The actor's mount is a camel, elk, horse, boar, woolly goat, or some other hoofed draft an\u0002imal.</li>\n<li>II) Molephant Mount - The actor's mount is a molephant or some other creature that can burrow or charge in tight quarters.</li>\n<li>III) Gigaphid Mount - The actor's mount is a gigaphid or some other massive intelligent creature that can fly.</li>\n</ul>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":true,"tiers":3,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pvssLwpEx0uuFLaq"}},"_id":"vhRoyYAqkSydmLhH"}
{"name":"Lowborn","type":"talent","img":"icons/magic/control/mouth-smile-deception-purple.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor is versed in dealing with societal outsiders, thanks to her upbringing and life experience. For a social skill check (e.g. Charm, Deception, Menace, or Performance) against serfs, vagrants, nomads, or members of the criminal underground, convert a single miss into 1 hit. This talent may not be used more than once against the same individual, and can only be used once against an organization targeted by social networking during downtime.</p>","purchaseCost":10,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.GTyCnoDKttPXr21i"}},"_id":"x2TaAhlahW2Ar9Vl"}
{"name":"Anodynamo","type":"talent","img":"icons/skills/wounds/anatomy-organ-heart-red.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor has a powerful adrenal response to pain and physical trauma. When she is critically wounded, she instantly restores 2 MP. When she is mortally wounded (or has a critical wound upgraded to a mortal wound), she instantly restores 2 MP.&nbsp;</p>","purchaseCost":15,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.wNijonCtqEngSGcm"}},"_id":"yQIQg92QC7dv8w0S"}
{"name":"Webspinner","type":"talent","img":"icons/creatures/webs/web-thin-pruple.webp","data":{"description":"<p>An actor can exploit her environment, utilizing nearby obstacles and hazards to amplify her aggression. She may burn 3 MP <em>before</em> making a melee or missile (but not magic) attack for the potential to do more damage. If her attack is successful, she makes a Traps skill check with the same task difficulty as her attack roll and adds each hit to the damage.</p>","purchaseCost":30,"tiered":false,"tiers":null,"currentTier":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"zER2pdCJ5klFAfnV":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Gl74zaukyStsNZNd"}},"_id":"zm8f889olfWxFUBQ"}
